      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, while the interior is pristine, featuring supple leather and untouched trim. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a smooth-running engine, crisp transmission shifts, and all systems functioning exactly as designed. This is a collector-grade example that has been meticulously maintained and requires nothing but a new owner who appreciates excellence.",
