      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard that warrants the 'mint' designation. This specimen remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior devoid of discernible wear. Meticulously preserved and mechanically superior, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a definitive example of the model. We invite you to experience a standard of automotive excellence that is increasingly difficult to source.",
