    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find a cleaner ride than this beauty. It\u2019s been absolutely babied since day one\u2014it literally looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love instantly. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
